程序包 io.github.kubesys.devfrk.annotation

注释类型 RequestMapping

@Target({TYPE,METHOD})
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Documented
public @interface RequestMapping
从以下版本开始:
2.0.1
作者:
wuheng@iscas.ac.cn

  • 可选元素概要

    可选元素
    修饰符和类型 可选元素 说明
    RequestMethod[] method
    The HTTP request methods to map to, narrowing the primary mapping: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE.
    String[] value
    The primary mapping expressed by this annotation.

  • 元素详细资料

    • value

      String[] value
      The primary mapping expressed by this annotation. For example, @RequestMapping("/foo").

      Supported at the type level as well as at the method level! When used at the type level, all method-level mappings inherit this primary mapping, narrowing it for a specific handler method.

      NOTE: A handler method that is not mapped to any path explicitly is effectively mapped to an empty path.

      返回:
      value
      默认值:
      {}

    • method

      RequestMethod[] method
      The HTTP request methods to map to, narrowing the primary mapping: GET, POST, PUT, DELETE.

      Supported at the type level as well as at the method level! When used at the type level, all method-level mappings inherit this HTTP method restriction.

      返回:
      method
      从以下版本开始:
      2.0.3
      默认值:
      {}
